# ⚔️ SkillVerse

SkillVerse is a Telegram-based Play-to-Earn gaming platform where players compete in skill-based games, earn MIM Points, climb leaderboards, unlock achievements, and participate in seasonal events.

## Features

- 🎮 Skill-based games
- ⚔️ PvP Battles
- 🪙 MIM Points
- 🏆 Leaderboards
- 🎁 Daily Rewards
- 👤 Warrior Profiles
- 🌌 Seasons
- 🏅 Hall of Fame
- 💰 Future Wallet Integration

